profile:
Nora Forsey has been working in design since she graduated from the International Academy in 1986.  She has successfully completed both residential and small commercial projects.
She is the winner of Toronto Community News 2010 Platinum Award for Interior Design.
Nora has a keen eye for colour, texture and space resulting in a distinctive, individual environment.
service_area: Toronto area, Vaughan area, Alliston area
